tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    category VARCHAR(100),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    stock_quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE SalesChannel (
    channel_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    channel_name VARCHAR(255),
    region VARCHAR(100),
    contact_name VARCHAR(255),
    contact_email VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE product_sales (
    sale_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    channel_id INT,
    sale_date DATE,
    quantity INT,
    total_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(product_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (channel_id) REFERENCES sales_channels(channel_id)
);

CREATE TABLE product_sales (
    product_id INT,
    channel_id INT,
    price DECIMAL(10,2),
    sale_date DATE,
    CONSTRAINT product_sales_pk PRIMARY KEY (product_id, channel_id, sale_date),
    CONSTRAINT product_sales_fk_product FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES product(product_id),
    CONSTRAINT product_sales_fk_channel FOREIGN KEY (channel_id) REFERENCES sales_channel(channel_id)
);

CREATE TABLE price_change_history (
    product_id INT,
    old_price DECIMAL(10,2),
    new_price DECIMAL(10,2),
    change_date TIMESTAMP,
    CONSTRAINT price_change_history_fk_product FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES product(product_id)
);

CREATE TABLE product_category (
    product_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (product_id, category_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(product_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES categories(category_id)
);

CREATE TABLE product_sales (
    product_id INT,
    channel_id INT,
    sale_date DATE NOT NULL,
    quantity INT NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(product_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (channel_id) REFERENCES sales_channels(channel_id)
);
